Rubens as collector of Bruegel. Rubens & Bruegel: 1) Peasants falling out at Cards; 2) Group on hill in technique Buckingham Palace St. George and Bruegel Sermon of St. John; 3) Harvest picture with Rainbow & Prag Haymaking; 4) Landscape treatment in A.S.
